    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/af3ca73b75f145a4b6bbb1feba6c3496.avif?t=1756125862\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage an Abandoned Farm </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/8158f4ddbd00833152ca579f67ec6dc8.poster.avif?t=1756125862\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/8158f4ddbd00833152ca579f67ec6dc8.webm?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/8158f4ddbd00833152ca579f67ec6dc8.mp4?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start in debt with an abandoned farm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant different seasonal crops, harvest, and sell them to customers or directly at the market</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and decorate the farm however you like!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Your Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/d4bab089cfaae7d772bc71615a062e78.poster.avif?t=1756125862\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/d4bab089cfaae7d772bc71615a062e78.webm?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/d4bab089cfaae7d772bc71615a062e78.mp4?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy a small shop in ruins and turn it into a successful business</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the variety of items sold as you produce them on the farm</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and decorate your shop to attract more and more customers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire and train employees to help you sell even more</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fair Expansion!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This road connects an important trade route, making it the perfect spot for a successful fair! Watch this small fair grow into an important and wealthy trade center!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help construct new buildings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell products at the fair</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a vast world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/4acc4b48c589b681c0ae5daefd693db6.poster.avif?t=1756125862\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/4acc4b48c589b681c0ae5daefd693db6.webm?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/4acc4b48c589b681c0ae5daefd693db6.mp4?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources to craft items and expand your farm</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different areas in search of rare items</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt animals and fight monsters to obtain valuable items</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore caves to obtain valuable ores. But be careful! The deeper you go, the more dangerous it gets!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get your dream home</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/7e4bae9afc75a148fc11e26f691f0221.poster.avif?t=1756125862\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/7e4bae9afc75a148fc11e26f691f0221.webm?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159000/extras/7e4bae9afc75a148fc11e26f691f0221.mp4?t=1756125862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand and furnish your house, creating the home of your dreams!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal Events</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seasonal events last one season (28 days) and can either hinder or help the player. They affect the world the player lives in:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Financial Crisis! The price of the products the player sells drops significantly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prosperous Season! During this season, the price the player can sell products for increases!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
